Netizen contribution
Students of the Second Affiliated Middle School of East China Normal University in Shanghai sent a joint open letter to the principal, protesting against a series of restrictive measures taken by the principal Zhou Bin after he took office, and demanding that he maintain the spirit of "freedom, democracy, and openness" of the Second Affiliated Middle School of East China Normal University
And requested:
1. Restore the tablet Zhixue.com APP:
2. Cancel the restrictions on the time and location of tablet use;
3. Optimize or replace the English dictionary for the tablet, such as Youdao Dictionary;
4. Cancel the hairstyle restriction;
5. In the future, major decisions need to be discussed and voted on by us, or give specific reasons after announcement for students to discuss and feedback.
